Class IDAREProperties

  • java.lang.Object
    • idare.Properties.IDAREProperties

extends Object

      • IDARE_NODE_UID

        public static final String IDARE_NODE_UID
        The ID for this node if it is the target of a link. At network creation this will be set to the SUID of the corresponding node. It should never ever be overwritten Link Nodes should (in general) not have this property set.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values
